# No External Communication Policy

This project is for personal use only. Do not add features that communicate with external services.

- Do not add third-party analytics, tracking pixels, ads, or telemetry.
- Do not add external SDKs or libraries that send requests outside this origin.
- Do not add API calls (`fetch`, XHR, WebSocket, EventSource, WebRTC, sendBeacon) to third-party domains.
- Keep runtime behavior self-contained with local logic, localStorage, and static assets in this repository.
- If a feature appears to require external communication, stop and ask the user for explicit approval first.

Allowed exception:

- Browser-managed update checks for this app's own Service Worker and same-origin static assets.
